OL,4,CNo need to swap data for drinks, says
OL,5,Cprivacy body
OL,6, Customers should think carefully about
OL,7, handing over personal data when
OL,8, ordering food and drink via their
OL,9, mobile phones, the UK's body overseeing
OL,10, data privacy suggests.
OL,12,FApp and web-based ordering has become
OL,13,Fcommonplace during the pandemic.
OL,15,FBut the Information Commissioner's
OL,16,FOffice told the BBC that customers
OL,17,Fshould be aware they had a choice over
OL,18,Fwhether to share information.
OL,20,FVenues should only ask for data that is
OL,21,F"relevant and necessary", the ICO said.
